title: Good Omens REACTION Series FINALE: The Very Last Day of the Rest of Their Lives Part 1
author: JK Reacts
comment: I love the comment of " he puts a lot of conditions on their relationship." it's very telling. Crowley is very open, even though if Hell finds out he'd be killed, but he still comes to Aziraphale's rescue all the time. Aziraphale is quite the bastard hahaha.
Netflix did respond to the petition demanding they scrap Good Omens by promising not to make any more.
According to David Tennant, 11:42 is the moment the Hell Hound bit him.
Darn a shock you gave me.. Here I am peacefully watching and then BAM "End of part 1" I jumped a meter in the air at least  😂
Oh yes.  Timing. Just logged out of WoW Classic to eat.
